# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .dockerignore — NexusBid API
#
# Excludes files that must NOT enter the Docker build context.
# Without this file every .env.* secret, the full .git history, and
# node_modules are sent to the Docker daemon on every build.
#
# Rule: exclude everything, then allow only what the build actually needs.
# The Dockerfiles explicitly COPY: package*.json, tsconfig.json, src/
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Version control ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# ── Node.js dependencies ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Always reinstalled inside the image via `npm ci`.
# Sending this folder would balloon the build context by hundreds of MB.
node_modules

# ── Build output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Rebuilt from source inside the image. Stale local dist/ must not leak in.
dist

# ── Environment files / Secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# CRITICAL: these files contain real credentials and must NEVER enter the image.
# Secrets are injected at runtime via `env_file` in Docker Compose or via
# AWS Secrets Manager / Parameter Store in production.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Tests ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
tests/
coverage/
.nyc_output/
junit.xml
jest.config.ts
tsconfig.test.json

# ── Logs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# ── Docker files (self-referential) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# No reason for compose files or Dockerfiles to exist inside their own image.
docker-compose*.yml
.dockerignore

# ── Editor / IDE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── OS-generated files ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── CI/CD ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.github/

# ── Misc project files (not needed at runtime) ────────────────────────────────
ecosystem.config.js
scripts/
*.md
README*
